data.title: University of Mary Washington
data.meta_description: At the University of Mary Washington, we’re committed to a college experience that focuses on what matters most.
data.text:
What Do They Say About Us?

One of America’s best colleges

– U.S. News and World Report

100% of classes taught by professors

One of the best and most interesting colleges

– Fiske Guide to Colleges

A top producer of U.S. Fulbright Scholars

Our Voices

Kathryn N. Warlick
